{"tid":2341301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"aespa《SBS歌謠大戰》服裝被批超俗！網讚BLACKPINK造型師好強大","createTime":"2020-12-26T08:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T03:29:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"320cbcf2aba90fdf16b022e9b84dfa167b8f7a54","tid":2341301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"南韓SM娛樂新女團aespa一舉一動都是關注焦點，昨（25）日4人出席《SBS歌謠大戰》，但站出來的服裝卻讓網友看傻眼，不但批評「超級土」、「平常音樂節目打歌服比年末舞台服裝還好看」，甚至有人想起也是4人組合的BLACKPINK，「突然覺得BP造型師好強大」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5358/d5358269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5358%2Fd5358269.jpg&h=a1dfd4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲aespa登上《SBS歌謠大戰》紅毯。（圖／翻攝自SBS官網）<br />\n<br />\naespa昨晚登上《SBS歌謠大戰in大邱》舞台，採事前預錄方式，4人先是踏上紅毯，分別穿著朱紅色、粉色、藍色與棗紅色的打歌服，在胸口處搭配亮片與蕾絲，成員Winter被問到當晚的服裝概念，笑笑回答說是「配合耶誕節的氣氛，把我們都裝飾成禮物的樣子。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5358/e5358272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5358%2Fe5358272.jpg&h=5235074c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼aespa《SBS歌謠大戰》服裝被批好土。（圖／翻攝自SBS官網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5358/e5358268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5358%2Fe5358268.jpg&h=d48e0fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過南韓論壇「Theqoo」對昨晚aespa的服裝有著熱烈迴響，「Cody（服裝造型師）真的很不怎樣」、「顏色超土，那亮亮東西的材質一看就是廉價品」、「平常音樂節目打歌服比年末舞台服裝還好看」、「不要因為是大舞台就特別用力做...像平常那樣就好了啊。」<br />\n<br />\n也有人比較起同樣是4名女孩組成的BLACKPINK，「衣服是漂亮，但出席這種年末舞台覺得水準還是低了點...這時突然覺得BP造型師真的很強大！」但也有人稱讚，「其實我覺得不差啊」、「上了舞台之後其實不錯，但在紅毯就覺得還好」掀起了討論。"},{"pid":"9e86231bbd4896194a77d200459964d8b6509012","tid":2341301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5358/d5358271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5358%2Fd5358271.jpg&h=6541db47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼aespa以相同服裝表演。（圖／翻攝自SBS官網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5358/d5358270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5358%2Fd5358270.jpg&h=a9ebdbd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8bd2b9dc4c2c0ef5875e803c3cf1b738258e717","tid":2341301,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"完蛋了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad295ff4d6f0412fff7a2dc6fa541d2f4583f78","tid":2341301,"uid":117318,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"隻支那雞陣支那味真係口罩都遮唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3ab368c81c179e34554f896f3946d2980914c9","tid":2341301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bd2b9dc4c2c0ef5875e803c3cf1b738258e717","tid":2341301,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"完蛋了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"TWICE&gt;aespa<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1b6002f6841dccd629269a8c0b82d3b558b442","tid":2341301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad295ff4d6f0412fff7a2dc6fa541d2f4583f78","tid":2341301,"uid":117318,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"隻支那雞陣支那味真係口罩都遮唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"咩00=joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f9a61ff64051d1a232cc9486ff4c9b51a745d5","tid":2341301,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96257dcd76b6f857126